tags.query:
SELECT a.[BATCHID] AS [BatchID]
,a.[ITEM_CODE] AS [ItemCode]
,a.[ITEM_DESC] AS [ItemDescription]	
,a.[QTY]
,a.[DATE_CREATED] AS [CreationTS]
,b.[RecipeNumber]
,a.[CLASS_CODE] AS [ClassCode]
,a.[STATION_LOC] AS [StationID]
,a.[STATION] AS [StationName]
,a.[CREATE_TS] AS [RecordedTS]
,b.[RecipeID]
,b.[RecipeName]
,b.[RecipeDescription]
,b.[LineName]
,b.[MachineName]
,b.[ClientNumber]
,b.[RecordedTS]
FROM [BatchData].[dbo].[tblBatches] a
INNER JOIN [BatchData].[dbo].[tblRecipe] b
ON a.[ITEM_CODE] = b.RecipeName 
WHERE CAST(a.[BATCHID] AS NVARCHAR) LIKE '{[.]selectedBatchID}'

eventScripts.script:
intValue = currentValue.value
	pathErrorTag = '[.]xError'
	
	if (intValue >= 90 and intValue < 100) or (intValue >= 900 and intValue < 1000):
		system.tag.writeBlocking([pathErrorTag], [True])
		shared.eventslib.writeIgnitionLogEntry("ChangedValue '%s' >> '%s'" 
									% (previousValue.value, intValue),1,str(tagPath))
	else:
		system.tag.writeBlocking([pathErrorTag], [False])
		system.tag.writeBlocking("[.]iStatePrev", previousValue.value)
